# Tailwind CSS Styling Guidelines

## General Principles

1. **Utility-First**: Use Tailwind utility classes directly in JSX
2. **Responsive Design**: Use responsive prefixes (`sm:`, `md:`, `lg:`, `xl:`, `2xl:`)
3. **Dark Mode**: Use `dark:` prefix for dark mode variants (configured in [tailwind.config.ts](mdc:tailwind.config.ts))

## Color System

This project uses CSS variables (HSL) for theming with shadcn/ui design tokens:

### Core Colors
- `background` / `foreground` - Base colors
- `card` / `card-foreground` - Card backgrounds
- `primary` / `primary-foreground` - Primary actions
- `secondary` / `secondary-foreground` - Secondary actions
- `muted` / `muted-foreground` - Muted/disabled states
- `accent` / `accent-foreground` - Accent highlights
- `destructive` / `destructive-foreground` - Error/delete actions

### Border & Input
- `border` - Border color
- `input` - Input border color
- `ring` - Focus ring color

Use with Tailwind classes:
```tsx
<div className="bg-background text-foreground border-border">
<button className="bg-primary text-primary-foreground">
```

## Common Patterns

### Responsive Layout
```tsx
<div className="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
```

### Button Styles
```tsx
<button className="rounded-full border border-solid transition-colors 
  hover:bg-[#f2f2f2] dark:hover:bg-[#1a1a1a] px-4 py-2">
```

### Card Component
```tsx
<div className="rounded-lg border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-800 
  p-6 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
```

### Center Content
```tsx
<div className="flex items-center justify-center min-h-screen">
```

## Custom Configuration

Extend Tailwind in [tailwind.config.ts](mdc:tailwind.config.ts) for:
- Custom colors
- Custom spacing
- Custom fonts
- Custom animations

## Font Variables

The project uses Geist fonts with CSS variables (configured in [layout.tsx](mdc:src/app/layout.tsx)):
- `--font-geist-sans` - Sans-serif font
- `--font-geist-mono` - Monospace font

Apply with: `font-[family-name:var(--font-geist-sans)]`
